{
  "stem": "11144.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she said, you know, you-- and she was-- there was a friend of my stepfather who converted way when, before the war, and they were giving me her as a example.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, she converted, so Jew didn't want her, and the Pole didn't want her.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that's why she stayed single.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- so-- you know, so she said, you see?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she was telling me the same story, this woman.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my mother says, you see, if you do this, you know, nobody will want you and da, da, da, da.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, you know, she was-- they were really brainwashing me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I couldn't break with it as long as I was in that town, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I felt ashamed that I was putting up-- whatever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I said, OK, when I go to the university, to Bratslav, I'm going to cut with all this junk.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And sure enough, I-- when I went to the university, to Bratslav, I-- I dropped all my friends, all my Polish friends at that time.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I got into a Jewish circle of friends and became, you know, very friendly.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We are still very friendly with-- with all of them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Three years.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Three--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Four years.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, because I went to the university there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From 1950-- no, I was there longer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was there from 1951 to 1956.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[INTERPOSING VOICES]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I think he survived as a Jew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was right after liberation, which was 19-- 1944.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't-- somebody must have taken me with horses and a buggy, or I walked.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because out there, what we did-- I mean, the distances were quite-- you know, and we had no transportation, so we walked.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We would go into the forest and start walking-- you know, we were walking.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
